                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner in charge with the glass.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going down Queen-street to my mother, and bought a halfpenny worth of sweet-stuff; a boy threw the glass into the road - the boy ran after me, and called another man.</p>
